text: Rudolf Beerbohm (3 November 1941 - 1 June 2018) was a German equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:2018 deaths Category:German male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of East Germany Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Mecklenburg-Vorpommern
